data.description: Welcome Home to this BREATHTAKING STUNNER!! Immediately upon entering the Inviting Courtyard, you will Fall In Love with the Fully Paved Circular Drive along with the Distinctive Custom Iron and Glass Front Entrance.  As you Transition into the Home, Prepare to be AMAZED as you Step into Pure Style and Sophistication!!  Upon Entering the Foyer you will Immediately be Drawn to the GORGEOUS Bamboo Wood Flooring, Grand Columns and Wood Beam Ceiling.  Stroll through the Well Designed, OPEN Main Living Space while you Notice the Cozy Fireplace with Custom Mantel, Custom Wood Shelving, Trendy Barn Door and Plenty of Windows Allowing for Copious amounts of Light. As you gravitate to the Kitchen you are sure to be IMPRESSED with the Gorgeous Granite Countertops, MASSIVE Island, Tasteful Lighting, Abundance of Beautiful Sleek Cabinets and Stainless-Steel Appliances. Make your way to the Owner's Retreat where you will find a Light and Bright Relaxing space with SPA Inspired En-Suite Featuring CUSTOM Granite Dual Vanity & Mirror, Roomy Soaking Tub with Beautifully Tiled Custom Accent Wall, LUXURIOUS Step-In Shower with Stunning Custom Tile Surround and Well-Appointed Large Custom Walk-In Closet, Fully Equipped with Shelving and Storage Space. This Home is Perfect for Entertaining or Relaxing Outside, Invite your guests outdoors to Indulge in Relaxation Under the Covered Patio while you Adore the Beautiful Landscaping and Sparking Pool. Option for 4 Garage Spaces with Additional Workshop or can be used at 5 Garage Spaces. Close to Kierland Commons, Shopping, Dining, Golfing, Freeways, Airport and So Much More!! Hurry to see this one, you are sure to be IMPRESSED!!!
